        "min": 10,
        "max": 5000,
        "value": 5000,
        "unit": "mm/s",
        "description": "High speeds minimize heat accumulation on low-thermal-conductivity rubber; slower for heavy contamination (1000-3000 mm/s), faster for light (5000-10000 mm/s). Recommended 5000 mm/s for balance. Source: Industry standards from Laserax equipment manuals; case studies in Journal of Cleaner Production (2020) for surface prep."
